        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "You can use the operation that this method returns only once to perform a search, but you can reuse the query that you provide. During execution, the operation performs a new search and returns the first batch of results. If there are more results available, you must create a separate query object using the provided cursor object. "
